## ⚡ Big Data Mode vs Demo Mode

StreamIQ supports **dual NLP engines**:

- **Big Data Mode (Spark NLP)**  
  Run distributed pipelines with PySpark + Spark NLP.  
  ```bash
  export NLP_ENGINE=spark
  python src/app.py

